e concludes with phase_cleanup() invoking G1ConcurrentMark::cleanup() to reclaim empty regions and finalize marking data structures, followed by concurrent_cycle_end() which completes timing and tracing of the marking cycle. This entire chain ensures that object liveness is tracked concurrently while maintaining SATB invariants, enabling efficient mixed-mode garbage collection that can quickly identify and evacuate low-efficiency old regions identified during marking."
